togramas |publisher=[[Hearst Magazines International]] |language=es}}</ref>\n\n==Cast==\n{{columnslist|\n* Darko Peric as Chiquitin\n* [[\u00c1lvaro Cervantes]] as Nacho\n* [[Ana Morgade]] as Directora del Banco\n* [[Cristina Casta\u00f1o]] as Arancha\n* [[S\u00edlvia Abril]] as Nadia\n* Sergio Torrico as Jefe de Bomberos\n* [[Malena Alterio]] as Lucia\n* [[Jordi S\u00e1nchez (actor)|Jordi S\u00e1nchez]] as Adrian\n* Dani Guzman as Dani\n* Jordi Aguilar as Cliente Concesionario\n* Mar\u00eda Alfonsa Rosso as Carmina\n* \u00c1lex de Lucas as Mensajero Tarta\n* Cristina Alarc\u00f3n as Lorena-Vendedora\n* Manuel Gancedo as Se\u00f1or Comprador\n* Dani Nieto as Hijo de Alex\n* Ya\u00ebl Belicha as Manuela-Vendedora\n* [[C\u00e9sar Camino]] as Camarero Restaurante Lujo\n* Nancy Yao as Traductora\n* Dulceida as Camarera Restaurante Mejicano\n* Almar G. Sato as Susan Wong\n* Mauricio Morales as Monitor de Puenting\n* Fabia Castro as Chica Airbnb\n* Gonzalo Villamizar as Ni\u00f1o Latino\n* Mike Lee as Jefazo Americano 2\n* Cristina Serrato as Clienta sexshop 2\n* Kao Chenmin as Mister Zhang\n* Chac\u00f3n Clara as Marina\n* Bea de la Cruz as Comercial AIRBNB 2\n* Patricia C\u00f3rdoba as Secretaria Nacho\n* Carlos Wu as Chino tienda comestibles\n* V\u00edctor Martinez as Andreas\n* Filipa Ribeiro as Dependienta\n* Paul Brennan as Jefazo Americano 1\n* Yohana Yara as Gladys\n* Oscar Reyes as Walter\n* Cindy Fuentes as Esteticienne\n* Gabriela Santos as Ni\u00f1a Latina\n}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{IMDb title|7853636}}\n\n[[Category:Spanish comedy films]]\n[[Category:2010s comedy films]]\n[[Category:Sony Pictures films]]\n[[Category:Films shot in Madrid]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|2019 film directed by Juana Mac\u00edas}}\n{{Infobox film\n| name = Under the Same Roof\n| film_name = {{Infobox name module|es|Bajo el mismo techo}}\n| director = Juana Mac\u00edas\n| writer = {{plainlist|\n* Daniel Corpas\n* Juana Mac\u00edas\n* Juan M